    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The use of what was originally a picture-symbol or hieroglyph of an object or being to represent phonetically the initial syllable or sound of the name of the object or being.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
